hi,我是给tomcat提bug的那位qiuboboy.

如果dubbo应用在容器中运行,dubbo没有提供容器销毁时的钩子,只用了shutdownhook.会导致上面的问题.

你可以在ServletContextListener#contextDestroyed里面调用:

```
final Class protocolConfig = Class.forName("com.alibaba.dubbo.config.ProtocolConfig");
final Method method = protocolConfig.getMethod("destroyAll");
 method.invoke(protocolConfig);
```

来主动关闭dubbo.

dubbo的优雅停机也有问题.我们内部版本已经修复.以后我们会把这些修改提交到dubbox上去.

建议shutdownhook最好也慎用,我们的应用会在容器关闭时,主动去调用shutdownhook.

```
   static {
    //add dubbo shutdown hook
    try {
        final Class protocolConfig = Class.forName("com.alibaba.dubbo.config.ProtocolConfig");
        final Method method = protocolConfig.getMethod("destroyAll");
        addShutdownHook(new Runnable() {
            @Override
            public void run() {
                try {
                    method.invoke(protocolConfig);
                } catch (Exception e) {
                    throw Exceptions.newRuntimeExceptionWithoutStackTrace(e);
                }
            }
        }, "DubboShutdownHook");
    } catch (Exception e) {
        //ignore
    }
}
```

static {
        Runtime.getRuntime().addShutdownHook(new Thread(new Runnable() {
            public void run() {
                if (logger.isInfoEnabled()) {
                    logger.info("Run shutdown hook now.");
                }
                ProtocolConfig.destroyAll();
            }
        }, "DubboShutdownHook"));
    }

如果ShutdownHook不能生效，可以自行调用：

ProtocolConfig.destroyAll();
